                "invention-title": [
                    "Device for preparing cement clinker and co-producing methane by sliding arc plasma fluidized bed",
                    "一种滑动弧等离子体流化床制备水泥熟料联产甲烷装置"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the technical field of cement production, and relates to a device for preparing cement clinker and co-producing methane by using a sliding arc plasma fluidized bed, the sliding arc plasma fluidized bed comprises a fluidized bed body, a blade electrode and an insulation sealing base, the insulation sealing base is arranged on a vibration part of a vibration device; the blade electrode is arranged on the lower portion in the fluidized bed body, the lower end of the fluidized bed body is provided with a carrier gas nozzle for spraying hydrogen, the fluidized bed body is provided with a feeding port higher than the blade electrode, and the upper end of the fluidized bed body is provided with a discharging port communicated with the clinker collecting device. The discharge port is used for outputting clinker and mixed gas, a gas outlet of the clinker collecting device is communicated with the electric heating reaction kettle, a gas outlet of the electric heating reaction kettle is communicated with the separation device, and the separation device is provided with a hydrogen outlet and a methane outlet. Methane can be co-produced while clinker is produced, carbon emission is effectively reduced, energy consumption is reduced, and clinker production efficiency is improved."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于水泥生产技术领域，涉及一种滑动弧等离子体流化床制备水泥熟料联产甲烷装置，其中滑动弧等离子体流化床包括流化床本体、刀片电极和绝缘密封底座，绝缘密封底座安装在振动装置的振动部件上，振动装置能驱动振动部件水平振动，刀片电极设于流化床本体内的下部，流化床本体下端设有喷入氢气的载气喷嘴，流化床本体上设有位置高于刀片电极的进料口，流化床本体上端设有连通熟料收集装置的出料口，出料口用于输出熟料和混合气体，熟料收集装置的出气口连通电加热反应釜，电加热反应釜的出气口连通分离装置，分离装置设有氢气出口和甲烷出口。本发明能在生产熟料的同时联产甲烷，有效降低碳排放，并降低能耗，提高熟料生产效率。"
                }
